    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the Penalty for NOT STOPPING after an Accident on the Highway by Driver",
        "additional_details": "In the Media there are cases every week now, this needs Controlling with adverts detailing the Penalty increase, it is a shame where things are going these days making life Cheap.\r\n\r\nLet\u2019s try and get things Changed.",
        "background": "There are far too many Drivers these days who HIT and RUN, at this time the Penalty is far too Low and needs a Large increase, many are Killed and it is Gutless Not to stop, I know some of these may have a reason like No Insurance or wanted by the Police, they are Cowards when the persons are dying",
